  • public class MyTermSpans
extends org.apache.lucene.search.spans.Spans
    Expert: Public for extension only. This does not work correctly for terms that indexed at position Integer.MAX_VALUE. Adapted from Lucene version: removed assert that interfered with testing using MockSpans.
